headline: POTTERY BARN TEEN INTRODUCES DORM CONCIERGE
summary: SAN FRANCISCO, May 15, 2025--Pottery Barn Teen, a portfolio brand of Williams-Sonoma, Inc., the world’s largest digital-first, design-led and sustainable home furnishings retailer, announced today the launch of Dorm Concierge, a new complimentary, personalized service designed to assist customers shopping for dorm products to Pick Up Near CampusTM.
